{"tid":875331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可能五六年後，香港已經不復存在","createTime":"2018-10-24T23:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T23:53:15.000Z","uid":14521,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bcfd763640d68b3d6c1d270105acabf4abeb6087","tid":875331,"uid":14521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"以往一大班一大班出現既雙非兒童，依家已經係小學高年班或者係初中，一口流利既普通話係香港走天下，望住店員已經習慣左同佢地用普通話對搭，香港人已經麻目了，換血計劃已經去到尾聲，當諗起連香港既教育局局長都質疑廣東話，建議大家用普通話個時，香港已經係末期語癌。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/074509_a724c509a349aaeafebbad2c14fa96ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F074509_a724c509a349aaeafebbad2c14fa96ab.png&h=f5bda29f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5b4b9d8ce888cf6596198de355af917d76029a","tid":875331,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T23:53:15.000Z","msg":"學好普通話 提早入中資公司做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環境你就無能力改變架啦 學班廢青鳩叫兩聲獨立就得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想繼續生存就改變自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}